{"tid":1946454,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[工會戰線] 工會戰線千奇唔好停啊!","createTime":"2020-03-27T15:34:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-27T16:00:49.000Z","uid":84408,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c010c0b43de579c97a543704bcfa3501d0efc66b","tid":1946454,"uid":84408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T15:34:53.000Z","msg":"我知有好多人可能比人炒 無工開<br />\n但經濟總會有好嘅一日<br />\n呢加更係時候饀光養晦<br />\n<br />\n我地盡力維持黃色經濟圈嘅運作<br />\n亦都應該趁機會加強工會嘅工作<br />\n唔係咁快就burn out<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大三罷唔係願景 佢係一定會發生的<br />\n我地唔會原諒黑警同呢個政權<br />\n<br />\n唯有組織先可以達至勝利<br />\n唯有組織先可以有力反抗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62b64bd13a7631f4b199a2f69437fcc32c5eccb9","tid":1946454,"uid":84408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T15:37:31.000Z","msg":"三大範疇都要繼續做<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f01919c8b0c45a976b17f6809acdc8a1f6ca976","tid":1946454,"uid":123615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T15:38:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1934796180b61166cba0462a5d7d620b907d2744","tid":1946454,"uid":84408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T15:40:04.000Z","msg":"自推<br />\n黃色經濟圈<br />\n工會<br />\n立會<br />\n制度內外都要繼續做<br />\n呢加放慢日後要追只會更難<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"009e97edded990635546f2c9355c96b158b37324","tid":1946454,"uid":84408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T15:42:26.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30425f078b1cf85ddba4abd011d0c83cd4aaf669","tid":1946454,"uid":84408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score"